full_title: Empty Out Your Pockets by Juice WRLD
title: Empty Out Your Pockets

description.plain:
“Empty Out Your Pockets“ is an upbeat and catchy track by the late Juice WRLD. On the Nick Mira production, the late rapper boasts about his wealth, status, and issues with fame, in his typical fashion.

The track’s release was confirmed by Epic Games via an Instagram post, in which they stated the track will premiere worldwide in Fortnite on November 30, 2024. On this day, Juice’s label added the song as the sixth track on the The Party Never Ends, his final posthumous album.
